description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_EN: Hong Kong West Kowloon Station Public Car Park now full
description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_CN: 香港西九龍站公眾停車場現已泊滿

2025-10-29T14:17:00.CONTENT_EN: Transport Department has received notification from MTR Corporation Limited that Hong Kong West Kowloon Station Public Car Park is now full. Please use public transport to reach the station.
2025-10-29T14:17:00.CONTENT_CN: 運輸署接獲港鐵公司通知， 香港西九龍站公眾停車場現已泊滿。請使用公共交通工具前往。

2025-10-29T15:53:00.CONTENT_EN: All car parks at West Kowloon Cultural District are full. Members of the public are encouraged to take public transport to the West Kowloon Cultural District.
2025-10-29T15:53:00.CONTENT_CN: 西九文化區內所有停車場現已泊滿車輛，前往西九文化區一帶的市民請使用公共交通工具。

description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_EN: Additional station stop for selected train trips
description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_CN: 個別列車車次新增站點

2025-10-30T18:14:00.CONTENT_EN:
As informed by the Chinese Mainland Railway Authorities, the following train trips will stop
at Nanshabei Station starting from 1 Nov, 2025:

From Hong Kong West Kowloon Station to Guangzhounan Station: G6508, G6536, G6538, G6588

From Guangzhounan Station to Hong Kong West Kowloon Station: G6505, G6509, 
G6527, G6537, G6583

From Zhaoqingdong Station to Hong Kong West Kowloon Station: G6579

Tickets are available for purchase through the 12306 official website (12306. cn) or mobile app; appointed travel agents; or at Hong Kong West Kowloon Station. 

For train schedules, please refer to the 12306 official website (12306. cn) or mobile app, or the High Speed Rail website or mobile app.
2025-10-30T18:14:00.CONTENT_CN:
中國內地鐵路單位通知，由2025年11月1日起，以下列車車次會停靠南沙北站：

由香港西九龍站前往廣州南站：G6508，G6536，G6538，G6588

由廣州南站前往香港西九龍站：G6505，G6509，G6527，G6537，G6583

由肇慶東站前往香港西九龍站：G6579

你可透過12306官方網站(12306.cn)或手機應用程式、指定代理或前往香港西九龍站購買列車車票。

有關列車服務詳情，請瀏覽12306官方網站(12306.cn)或手機應用程式、高速鐵路網頁及手機應用程式。

description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_EN: Suspension of advance ticket sales for selected train trips
description.INCIDENT_DETAIL_CN: 個別列車車次暫停預售

2025-10-30T20:18:00.CONTENT_EN:
As informed by the Chinese Mainland Railway Authorities, advance ticket sales for the train trips travelling between Hong Kong West Kowloon Station and Guangzhoudong Station for 3 Nov and onwards will be suspended. 

For the latest advance ticket sales arrangements, please refer to the 12306 official website (12306. cn) and mobile app, High Speed Rail website and mobile app.
2025-10-30T20:18:00.CONTENT_CN:
中國內地鐵路單位通知，11月3日及以後來往香港西九龍站及廣州東站的列車車次會暫停預售。

有關最新預售安排，請留意12306官方網站(12306.cn)及手機應用程式、高速鐵路網頁及手機應用程式。

2025-10-31T20:42:00.CONTENT_EN: All car parks at West Kowloon Cultural District are full. Members of the public are encouraged to take public transport to the West Kowloon Cultural District.
2025-10-31T20:42:00.CONTENT_CN: 西九文化區內所有停車場現已泊滿車輛，前往西九文化區一帶的市民請使用公共交通工具。
